name: Arcade II
overview: A compilation of four games all previously released, and apparently re-named and used without permission. The four games are: Mushroom Masher, a centipede clone (previously released as Myriad), Squirm Tracks, a game where you re-arrange a maze on screen to get your worm from one end to another (previously released as Tricky Tracks), Clown Around, a breakout/clowns and balloons style game (previously released as Stunt Clown), and Balloon Ranger, a shooter previously released as Balloon.
